Twist of Fate
FlavourText: The landscape twists before your eyes, morphing into realms of unspeakable horror.

Name: Wellspring of Creation
FlavourText:
The waters of life roil and flow,
birthing horrors of flesh and marrow.

Name: Dance of Destruction
FlavourText:
Atlassian aberrations engage in a deadly dance.
Will you be joining them in the fray?

Name: Stream of Consciousness
FlavourText: In a realm where thought is given form, action and will become one and the same.

Name: Singular Focus
FlavourText: You fancy yourself a god. You see only what you want to see.

Name: Wandering Path
FlavourText:
Embrace the journey, Nomad, for there is no destination.
This is the prime inescapable truth of eternity.

Name: Grand Design
FlavourText:
Ignore everything but your obsession, Nomad.
A mortal life is too short a season to entertain distractions.

Name: Cosmic Wounds
FlavourText: A single act of love and defiance may cascade destruction across the cosmos.

Name: Throw the Gauntlet
FlavourText: You must rise from mere amusement to respected equal.

Name: Memento Mori
FlavourText: When memories become twisted by a corrupted mind, history is rewritten, time after time.

Name: The Perfect Storm
FlavourText: Agony born of ennui. Hate born of love.

Name: Thirst for Knowledge
FlavourText: Constellations are systematically incinerated in the wake of an ever-expanding archive of minds.

Name: Insatiable Appetite
FlavourText: At the core of the mass, a fierce hunger seethes, as the Tangle's champion devours a myriad of worlds...

Name: Height of Hubris
FlavourText:
It takes either immense courage or unfettered masochism
to invoke unspeakable horrors, time after time...

Name: Captivated Interest
FlavourText: You had her curiosity. Now you have her attention.

Name: Eldritch Gaze
FlavourText:
You were drunk on the power of the cosmos,
until a hideous gaze settled upon you,
and tendrils began to unfurl...

Name: Wrath of the Cosmos
FlavourText: A fiery dawn illumines the horizon, and it becomes apparent that all that glitters is not gold...

Name: Shadow Shaping
FlavourText: In lieu of happiness, sometimes the absence of pain is good enough.

Name: Valley of Darkness
FlavourText:
Darkening mists shroud the pale sky,
blurring the barrier between nightmare and dream.

Name: Inevitable Ambush
FlavourText: The hunter must become the hunted.
